g promotional emails, newsletters, or SMS alerts</p></div></li></ul><div class=" mx-auto px-4 py-6"><h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">How We Use Your Information</h2><p>We use your data for the following purposes:</p></div><ul class="space-y-4"><li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed"><span class="min-w-[18px] min-h-[18px] mt-1 text-red"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 512 512" height="18" width="18" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M256 56c110.532 0 200 89.451 200 200 0 110.532-89.451 200-200 200-110.532 0-200-89.451-200-200 0-110.532 89.451-200 200-200m0-48C119.033 8 8 119.033 8 256s111.033 248 248 248 248-111.033 248-248S392.967 8 256 8zm0 168c-44.183 0-80 35.817-80 80s35.817 80 80 80 80-35.817 80-80-35.817-80-80-80z"></path></svg></span><div><p class="text-sm">To process and manage your travel bookings</p><p class="text-sm">To provide tailored recommendations and travel packages</p><p class="text-sm">To communicate important travel-related updates or changes</p><p class="text-sm">To respond to inquiries or support requests</p><p class="text-sm">To send promotional offers (only if you’ve opted in)</p><p class="text-sm">To improve our website, services, and customer experience</p><p class="text-sm">To comply with legal obligations and protect our business</p></div></li></ul><div class=" mx-auto px-4 py-6"><h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">How We Share Your Information</h2><p>We do not sell or rent your personal data. We may share your information with:</p></div><ul class="space-y-4"><li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed"><span class="min-w-[18px] min-h-[18px] mt-1 text-red"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 512 512" height="18" width="18" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M256 56c110.532 0 200 89.451 200 200 0 110.532-89.451 200-200 200-110.532 0-200-89.451-200-200 0-110.532 89.451-200 200-200m0-48C119.033 8 8 119.033 8 256s111.033 248 248 248 248-111.033 248-248S392.967 8 256 8zm0 168c-44.183 0-80 35.817-80 80s35.817 80 80 80 80-35.817 80-80-35.817-80-80-80z"></path></svg></span><div><p class="text-md font-bold">Trusted Service Providers</p><p class="text-sm">Third-party partners that assist with:</p><p class="text-sm">Payment processing</p><p class="text-sm">Booking management systems</p><p class="text-sm">Customer support tools</p><p class="text-sm">Marketing and email delivery</p><p class="text-sm">Data analytics tools (e.g., Google Analytics)</p></div></li><li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed"><span class="min-w-[18px] min-h-[18px] mt-1 text-red"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 512 512" height="18" width="18" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M256 56c110.532 0 200 89.451 200 200 0 110.532-89.451 200-200 200-110.532 0-200-89.451-200-200 0-110.532 89.451-200 200-200m0-48C119.033 8 8 119.033 8 256s111.033 248 248 248 248-111.033 248-248S392.967 8 256 8zm0 168c-44.183 0-80 35.817-80 80s35.817 80 80 80 80-35.817 80-80-35.817-80-80-80z"></path></svg></span><div><p class="text-md font-bold">Legal or Regulatory Authorities</p><p class="text-sm">When required by law, subpoena, or government request.</p></div></li><li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed"><span class="min-w-[18px] min-h-[18px] mt-1 text-red"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 512 512" height="18" width="18" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M256 56c110.532 0 200 89.451 200 200 0 110.532-89.451 200-200 200-110.532 0-200-89.451-200-200 0-110.532 89.451-200 200-200m0-48C119.033 8 8 119.033 8 256s111.033 248 248 248 248-111.033 248-248S392.967 8 256 8zm0 168c-44.183 0-80 35.817-80 80s35.817 80 80 80 80-35.817 80-80-35.817-80-80-80z"></path></svg></span><div><p class="text-md font-bold">Business Transfers</p><p class="text-sm">In the case of a merger, acquisition, or sale, your data may be transferred to the new entity.</p></div></li></ul><div class=" mx-auto px-4 py-6"><h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Data Security</h2><p>We use administrative, technical, and physical safeguards to protect your personal data from unauthorized access, alteration, or destruction. While we strive to ensure data security, no system is 100% secure. Some measures we employ include:</p></div><ul class="space-y-4"><li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed"><span class="min-w-[18px] min-h-[18px] mt-1 text-red"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 512 512" height="18" width="18" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M256 56c110.532 0 200 89.451 200 200 0 110.532-89.451 200-200 200-110.532 0-200-89.451-200-200 0-110.532 89.451-200 200-200m0-48C119.033 8 8 119.033 8 256s111.033 248 248 248 248-111.033 248-248S392.967 8 256 8zm0 168c-44.183 0-80 35.817-80 80s35.817 80 80 80 80-35.817 80-80-35.817-80-80-80z"></path></svg></span><div><p class="text-sm">HTTPS encryption across our website</p><p class="text-sm">Secure servers and firewall protection</p><p class="text-sm">Access control and employee confidentiality agreements</p></div></li></ul><div class=" mx-auto px-4 py-6"><h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Your Data Protection Rights</h2><p>Depending on your location, you may have the following rights:</p></div><ul class="space-y-4"><li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed"><span class="min-w-[18px] min-h-[18px] mt-1 text-red"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 512 512" height="18" width="18" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M256 56c110.532 0 200 89.451 200 200 0 110.532-89.451 200-200 200-110.532 0-200-89.451-200-200 0-110.532 89.451-200 200-200m0-48C119.033 8 8 119.033 8 256s111.033 248 248 248 248-111.033 248-248S392.967 8 256 8zm0 168c-44.183 0-80 35.817-80 80s35.817 80 80 80 80-35.817 80-80-35.817-80-80-80z"></path></svg></span><div><p class="text-sm"><strong>Right to access –</strong> Request a copy of your personal data.</p><p class="text-sm"><strong>Right to rectification –</strong> Ask us to correct inaccurate or incomplete data.</p><p class="text-sm"><strong>Right to erasure – </strong> Request deletion of your data under certain conditions.</p><p class="text-sm"><strong>Right to restrict processing – </strong> Ask us to limit the use of your data.</p><p class="text-sm"><strong>Right to data portability –</strong> Receive your data in a commonly used format.</p><p class="text-sm"><strong>Right to object –</strong> Object to data processing for marketing purposes.</p><p class="text-sm"><strong>Right to withdraw consent –</strong> Revoke consent for any data use based on consent.</p></div></li></ul><div class=" mx-auto px-4 py-6"><h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">International Data Transfers</h2><p>If you are accessing our services from outside India, please note that your data may be transferred to and processed in India or other countries. We ensure such transfers comply with applicable data protection laws.</p></div><div class=" mx-auto px-4 py-6"><h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Retention of Data</h2><p>We retain your data only as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes described above, including any legal or accounting requirements.</p></div><div class=" mx-auto px-4 py-6"><h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Children’s Privacy</h2><p>Our services are not directed to individuals under the age of 18. We do not knowingly collect personal information from minors.</p></div><div class=" mx-auto px-4 py-6"><h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Policy Updates</h2><p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in law or our practices. The latest version will always be available on this page with an updated revision date.</p></div><div class=" mx-auto px-4 py-6"><h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Contact Us</h2><p>For questions, requests, or concerns regarding your privacy or this policy, please contact:</p><a href="/contact"><button class="mt-8 px-6 py-3 bg-[#E76F51] text-white text-sm rounded-full hover:bg-[#d65a3f] transition shadow-lg">Contact Us</button></a></div></div></div></section><div id="footer" class="footer mt-0"><footer class="bg-gradient-to-b from-[#102E50] to-[#000000] text-white pt-12" id="footer"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 pb-20"><div class="flex flex-wrap justify-between gap-12 pb-12 border-b border-blue-700"><div class="w-full md:w-1/4 text-center md:text-left"><a class="inline-block mb-4" href="/"><img alt="Travelxploria" loading="lazy" width="180" height="20" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="mx-auto md:mx-0" style="color:transparent" srcSet="/images/logo-footer.png 1x, /images/logo-footer.png 2x" src="https://www.travelxploria.com/images/logo-footer.png"/></a><div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-sm mt-2 md:mt-0">Travelxploria (unit of Explorer Club Holidays)</div><div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 mt-2 md:mt-0"></div><div class="flex justify-center md:justify-start gap-4 mt-6"><a class="text-[#ff886f] text-xl"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M13.397 20.997v-8.196h2.765l.411-3.209h-3.176V7.548c0-.926.258-1.56 1.587-1.56h1.684V3.127A22.336 22.336 0 0 0 14.201 3c-2.444 0-4.122 1.492-4.122 4.231v2.355H7.332v3.209h2.753v8.202h3.312z"></path></svg></a><a class="text-[#ff886f] text-xl"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M19.633 7.997c.013.175.013.349.013.523 0 5.325-4.053 11.461-11.46 11.461-2.282 0-4.402-.661-6.186-1.809.324.037.636.05.973.05a8.07 8.07 0 0 0 5.001-1.721 4.036 4.036 0 0 1-3.767-2.793c.249.037.499.062.761.062.361 0 .724-.05 1.061-.137a4.0